Use,Purist,it,in,app,Chat,API,to,add,chat,support,for,mobile,apps,The,API,is,RESTful,and,uses,JSON,endpoints,with,an,API,Key,for,authorization,The,API,is,compatible,with,both,iOS,and,Android,push,notification,enabled,and,includes,a,backend,portal,for,customer,service,agents,See,the,API,docs,for,more,information,and,to,get,started,integrating,chat,into,your,mobile,apps